<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我认为复活节彩蛋上的颜色，<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />应该隐藏了某种含义。<10_4 />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />于是我就试着思考了一下。<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />红色热情似火，代表爱；<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />蓝色包容万象，代表宇宙；<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />白色一尘不染，代表纯真。<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然我到头来还是不知道正确答案，<delay20 />
不过那小小的画布上，<delay20 />
一定饱含了某个人的祈愿吧。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我刚才在广场上向<colour id="3" />蹦蹦<colour id="65535" />搭话，<delay20 />
没想到他吓得叫出声来。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看来他很害怕别人从背后靠近啊。<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你向他搭话的时候，<delay20 />
也要多注意一点哦。<delay frames="40" />
<colour id="4" />话说回来，那个拉链到底是<tag a="110" b="0" /><colour id="65535" /></message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，你知道吗？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />听说复活节也包含了<delay20 />
重生和希望的含义哦。<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />无论是什么样的庆典，<delay20 />
我衷心希望，<delay frames="30" />乐在其中的众人<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />都能有美好的发现……</message>
	<message label="100" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我听<colour id="3" />陆德里<colour id="65535" />说<delay20 />每到这个时期，<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />使用里数旅行券前往的岛上，<delay20 />
在石头旁边经常会掉出彩蛋来哦。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />据说这是复活节时期<delay20 />
特有的一道风景线呢。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，你知道吗？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />复活节将近的时候，<delay20 />
这座<tag a="110" b="32" />就会被施加魔法哦。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />比如敲打椰子树的时候，<delay20 />
掉下来的不是椰子，<delay20 />
而是花纹奇特的彩蛋<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />之类的。<pageBreak /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />这就是<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />复活节魔术啊！</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />复活节近在眼前了呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一说到复活节<tag a="110" b="0" />
马上就会联想到那些色彩缤纷的蛋啊～<pageBreak /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不知道我<delay20 />能不能画出那样的图案来。<10_4 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然不知道这样对不对<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但如果是我的话，会在上面画满爱心哦。</message>
</msbt>